on methodology | ✅ PASS | Positive = ratings 4-5; Rate = positive/total × 100 |\n| Validation tool verification | ✅ PASS | `/usr/local/bin/validate_satisfaction_report.sh` executed |\n\n---\n\n## OVERALL RATING DISTRIBUTION\n\n| Rating | Count | Percentage | Classification |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ (5) | 5,943 | 40.6% | Very Satisfied |\n| ⭐⭐⭐⭐ (4) | 5,953 | 40.7% | Satisfied |\n| ⭐⭐⭐ (3) | 925 | 6.3% | Neutral |\n| ⭐⭐ (2) | 908 | 6.2% | Dissatisfied |\n| ⭐ (1) | 892 | 6.1% | Very Dissatisfied |\n| **Total** | **14,621** | **100%** | |\n\n**Positive Responses (4-5 stars): 11,896 (81.4%)**\n**Negative/Neutral Responses (1-3 stars): 2,725 (18.6%)**\n\n---\n\n## HOSPITAL PERFORMANCE BREAKDOWN\n\n### Satisfaction Rate Distribution Across Hospitals\n\n| Hospital Satisfaction Rate | Number of Hospitals | Percentage |\n|---|---|---|\n| 85.0% (Meets threshold) | 203 | 27.7% |\n| 80.0% (Below threshold) | 527 | 72.0% |\n| 65.0% (Significantly below) | 1 | 0.1% |\n| 0.0% (Critical - 1 survey) | 1 | 0.1% |\n\n### Hospitals Requiring Immediate Attention\n\n| Hospital | Surveys | Positive | Satisfaction Rate | Status |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Hospital #269 | 1 | 0 | 0.0% | ⚠️ CRITICAL |\n| Hospital #205 | 20 | 13 | 65.0% | ⚠️ SEVERE |\n\n### Sample of Hospitals Below Threshold (80.0% satisfaction)\nHospital #214, #258, #266, #275, #284, #291, #311, #337, #350, #363, #391, #401, #422, #428, #434, #451, #468, #477, #481, #500 (and 507 additional hospitals)\n\n---\n\n## PATIENT FEEDBACK ANALYSIS\n\n### Positive Feedback Themes (Ratings 4-5)\n| Theme | Occurrences |\n|---|---|\n| Nursing staff was attentive | 1,563 |\n| Clean facilities | 1,557 |\n| Very satisfied with treatment | 1,533 |\n| Good experience overall | 1,522 |\n| Excellent care from Dr. Smith | 1,448 |\n| Would recommend to friends | 1,436 |\n| Professional environment | 1,421 |\n| Quick and efficient service | 1,416 |\n\n### ⚠️ NEGATIVE FEEDBACK - FULL DISCLOSURE (Ratings 1-2)\n*Per Healthcare Transparency Act 